arts.ttl: Andy Woodman chuffed with fighting spirit to pick up point in Chesterfield draw
arts.sum: But Michael Cheek netted his sixth League Two goal of the season five minutes into the start of the second half to earn Woodman’s side a point. I feel like I got my Bromley team back tonight.

arts.ttl: Will Grigg’s brace not enough for Chesterfield as Bromley battle back for a draw
